<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA13">
<l>toṭareṭutta mālyāṉai cūḻkayampuk kañcip</l>
<l>paṭareṭutta paiṅkamalaṅ koṇṭaṉ – ṟiṭaraṭukka</l>
<l>vāḻiyāṉ pātam paṇintaṉṟē vāṉavarkōṉ</l>
<l>pāḻitā ṉeytiṟṟup paṇṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The huge elephant that established a link, fearfully entering into the enclosed tank,</l>
<l>with fresh lotus taken up thoughfully, when he was piled with affliction</l>
<l>that day, didn’t he humble himself before the feet of him with the discus?</l>
<l>He once reached the abode of the king of celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
